uk.azdev.openfire.net.attrvalues

Class Int32AttributeValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.azdev.openfire.net.attrvalues.Int32AttributeValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeValue<java.lang.Long>

    public class Int32AttributeValue
extends java.lang.Object
implements AttributeValue<java.lang.Long>
    Represents an unsigned 32-bit value. The methods for getting and setting values in this class take long integers to compensate for Java's lack of unsigned types, but boundary conditions are still enforced.
    Author:
    Iain
